* Credibility
.background images/GOOGLE-02.png
- Does site offer github/linkedin - is it credible
- Do they list contact address?
- Can you verify via multiple channels
- Are they legal?
- What can you find if you google?
- Do they promote the business or profit opportunity ?
- Website have a lot of errors / bad links etc?
